hly-boosted final states are important as the\nsensitivity to new particles is extended to higher masses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 11 Jun 2017 21:25:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Nov 2017 14:42:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-22"}
