 to the noise power, and the tolerance can be automatically set.\nThe experiments confirm the efficiency of the proposed method even under\nconditions with high reverberation levels and intense noise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jun 2017 14:13:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-15"}
